headline: Wells Fargo Edges Up Nutrien (NYSE:NTR) Price Target, Keeps Cautious Stance Amid Fertilizer Market Recovery
summary: Nutrien Ltd. (NYSE:NTR) is one of the best commodity stocks to buy. Though the rating remained unchanged, the upward revision suggests a slight improvement in Wells Fargo’s view of Nutrien’s near-term prospects. […]
